## Summary
This documentation page explains how to build charts in Amplitude by adding events to the Event Module, using event properties to refine analysis, and applying conditions through filtering and grouping. It details the three main modules of Amplitude charts (Event, Measured As, and Segment By), explains default events, and demonstrates how to use wildcards for event searches.

